metadata.name: Sinise Tunne
metadata.description:
'Sinise Tunne' translating from Estonian to English - 'Feeling Blue'. 
Kalevipoeg is unsure of his identity and place in the world. He is feeling the pressure of just becoming King of Estonia and has been burdened with the task of saving the world. With this hanging above his head he feels alone and incapable, but this is just  the beginning of his journey.
